'''三佛齊航空182號班機空难'''發生於2021年1月9日，一架隸屬於[[三佛齊航空|三佛齊航空]]的[[波音|波音]][[波音737#737-500|737-524]]飞机自[[印尼|印尼]][[雅加達|雅加達]][[蘇加諾-哈達國際機場|蘇加諾-哈達國際機場]]起飛，計劃飛往[[印尼|印尼]][[坤甸|坤甸]][[蘇巴迪奧國際機場|蘇巴迪奧國際機場]]。起飛四分鐘后客機失聯，官方消息稱班机在機場以北{{cvt|19|km}}的{{link-en|千岛群岛 (印度尼西亞)|Thousand Islands (Indonesia)|千岛群岛}}{{link-id|拉基島|Pulau Laki}}附近坠入[[爪哇海|爪哇海]]中<ref>{{cite news|author=Kadek Melda Luxiana|url=https://news.detik.com/berita/d-5327287/pesawat-sriwijaya-air-hilang-kontak-di-pulau-lancang-kepulauan-seribu|title=Pesawat Sriwijaya Air Hilang Kontak di Pulau Lancang Kepulauan Seribu|date=2021-01-09|access-date=2021-01-09|work=detiknews.com|language=id|archive-date=2021-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109101732/https://news.detik.com/berita/d-5327287/pesawat-sriwijaya-air-hilang-kontak-di-pulau-lancang-kepulauan-seribu|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.airlive.net/breaking-sriwijaya-air-sj182-boeing-737-disappeared-from-radars-after-takeoff/ |title=A Boeing 737-500 disappeared from radars shortly after takeoff from Jakarta |accessdate=2021-01-09 |archive-date=2021-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109104253/https://www.airlive.net/breaking-sriwijaya-air-sj182-boeing-737-disappeared-from-radars-after-takeoff/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

客機載有62人，據報均爲[[印度尼西亞人|印度尼西亞公民]]。調查工作進行中，有關當局已在客機墜毀海域發現大片漏油、機體碎片、[[黑盒子|黑盒子]]、死者遗体及乘客的隨身物品<ref>{{Cite web|title=15 Fakta Terkini Pesawat Sriwijaya Air Jatuh di Kepulauan Seribu|url=https://news.detik.com/berita/d-5327463/15-fakta-terkini-pesawat-sriwijaya-air-jatuh-di-kepulauan-seribu|accessdate=2021-01-09|last=detikcom|first=Tim|work=detiknews|language=id-ID|archive-date=2021-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210923081401/https://news.detik.com/berita/d-5327463/15-fakta-terkini-pesawat-sriwijaya-air-jatuh-di-kepulauan-seribu|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://udn.com/news/story/6809/5161325|accessdate=2021-01-09|date=20210109T184905Z|work=聯合新聞網|title=印尼波音737客機墜毀 機上62人下落不明|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2021-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210923081438/https://udn.com/news/story/6809/5161325|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=印尼媒体：失联客机确定已坠毁|url=https://news.ifeng.com/c/82tUUCtoLrq|accessdate=2021-01-09|work=news.ifeng.com|archive-date=2021-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210923081356/https://news.ifeng.com/c/82tUUCtoLrq|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="新华网1">{{cite web |title=印尼失联客机坠毁位置找到，机上无中国籍乘客 |url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/mil/2021-01/10/c_1210972899.htm |website=新华网 |accessdate=2021-01-10 |archive-date=2021-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210923081451/http://www.xinhuanet.com/mil/2021-01/10/c_1210972899.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=jk>{{cite news |date=2021-01-11 |title=总统向空难者表示深切哀悼 搜救联队已确定飞机残骸和黑盒位置 |url=http://guojiribao.com/shtml/gjrb/20210111/58823.shtml |newspaper=印尼国际日报 |location= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210219054147/http://guojiribao.com/shtml/gjrb/20210111/58823.shtml |archivedate=2021-02-19 |accessdate=2021-01-11 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name=re>{{Cite web|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-indonesia-crash/indonesia-hopes-to-retrieve-black-boxes-of-crashed-jet-from-java-sea-idUSKBN29G00F|accessdate=2021-01-11|date=JANUARY 11, 2021|work=Reuters|title=Indonesia hopes to retrieve black boxes of crashed jet from Java Sea|language=en|archive-date=2021-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210923084914/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-indonesia-crash/indonesia-hopes-to-retrieve-black-boxes-of-crashed-jet-from-java-sea-idUSKBN29G00F|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2021年1月21日，印尼当局停止了对幸存者的搜救工作，机上62人已被认定全部遇难<ref name=Re2/>。至少58位遇难者的身份已被警方确认，其中包括班机机长<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://megapolitan.kompas.com/read/2021/01/29/20464211/3-korban-sriwijaya-air-sj-182-teridentifikasi-salah-satunya-pilot-kapten|title=3 Korban Sriwijaya Air SJ 182 Teridentifikasi, Salah Satunya Pilot Kapten Afwan|first=Kompas Cyber|last=Media|website=KOMPAS.com|access-date=2021-01-31|archive-date=2021-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210923081416/https://megapolitan.kompas.com/read/2021/01/29/20464211/3-korban-sriwijaya-air-sj-182-teridentifikasi-salah-satunya-pilot-kapten|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 失事飛機 ==
失事飛機型號為[[波音737#737-500|波音737-524]]，註冊編號為{{lang|en|PK-CLC}}（{{lang|en|{{abbr|MSN|製造商序列號（Manufacturer's Serial Number）}} 27323/2616}}）。1994年客機出厂被交付於[[美国大陆航空|美国大陆航空]]，當時其注冊號為{{lang|en|N27610}}，并于同年5月13日首次飛行。曾于2008年加装了翼尖小翼。2010年，美國大陸航空與[[聯合航空|美联航]]合并，客機獲轉移至美聯航旗下運營。2012年5月15日，三佛齐航空買下涉事客機，此客機亦爲三佛齊航空同年接收的15架波音737-500中的首架。事發時飛機機齡27年<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Sriwijaya Air flight #SJ182 lost more than 10.000 feet of altitude in less than one minute, about 4 minutes after departure from Jakarta.|url=https://twitter.com/flightradar24/status/1347850078644563969|accessdate=|author=Flightradar24|date=|format=|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2021-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109101849/https://twitter.com/flightradar24/status/1347850078644563969|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="asn">{{cite web|title=Accident description Sriwijaya Air Flight 182|url=https://aviation-safety.net/database/record.php?id=20210109-0|publisher=[[Aviation_Safety_Network|Aviation Safety Network]]|accessdate=2021-01-09|archive-date=2021-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211205013854/https://aviation-safety.net/database/record.php?id=20210109-0|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Sriwijaya launches new livery and 2 class service|url=http://www.gerryairways.com/index.php/en/sriwijaya-launches-new-livery-and-2-class-service/|access-date=2021-01-09|archive-date=2020-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200119045856/http://www.gerryairways.com/index.php/en/sriwijaya-launches-new-livery-and-2-class-service/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该机搭载兩具{{lang|en|[[CFM56#CFM56-3系列|CFMI CFM56-3B1]]}}引擎，飛機名稱為“{{lang|en|Citra}}”（[[印尼语|印尼语]]“象征”、“印象”之意）<ref name="auto">{{Cite web |title=PK-CLC Sriwijaya Air Boeing 737-524(WL) |url=https://www.planespotters.net/airframe/boeing-737-500-pk-clc-sriwijaya-air/rovwz3 |access-date=2021-01-09 |website=Planespotters.net |archive-date=2021-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109161027/https://www.planespotters.net/airframe/boeing-737-500-pk-clc-sriwijaya-air/rovwz3 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
