== 事故经过 ==
当日天气有雷雨<ref>{{cite web |title=Tangerang, Banten, Indonesia Weather History |url=https://www.wunderground.com/history/daily/id/tangerang/WIII/date/2021-1-9 |website=wunderground.com |accessdate=2021-01-10 |archive-date=2021-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210923083151/https://www.wunderground.com/history/daily/id/tangerang/WIII/date/2021-1-9 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。182號航班原定于[[印度尼西亚标准时间|印度尼西亚西部时间]]下午1時25分从蘇加諾-哈達國際機場起飞，预计下午3時正抵達蘇巴迪奧國際機場。在{{lang|en|2D}}航站楼完成[[后推|后推]]后，客機于下午2時36分在{{lang|en|25R}}跑道起飞，延误超過一个小时，预计到达时间也因此延后至下午3時50分<ref name="ANTV">{{cite web|last=antvklik.com|date=2021-01-09|title=Antvklik|url=https://www.antvklik.com/headline/berikut-foto-daftar-nama-penumpang-sriwijaya-air-sj-182-yang-hilang-kontak|access-date=2021-01-10|publisher=ANTV|language=id-ID|archive-date=2021-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109161309/https://www.antvklik.com/headline/berikut-foto-daftar-nama-penumpang-sriwijaya-air-sj-182-yang-hilang-kontak|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Pesawat Sriwijaya Air SJ182 Jakarta-Pontianak Hilang Kontak Berisi 56 Penumpang|url=https://www.merdeka.com/peristiwa/pesawat-sriwijaya-air-sj182-jakarta-pontianak-hilang-kontak-berisi-56-penumpang.html|access-date=2021-01-09|website=merdeka.com|language=id|archive-date=2021-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109105152/https://www.merdeka.com/peristiwa/pesawat-sriwijaya-air-sj182-jakarta-pontianak-hilang-kontak-berisi-56-penumpang.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

