离陆后，飞机得到升至{{cvt|1=29,000|2=ft|3=m}}高度的许可，正爬升至{{cvt|13000|ft}}時突然右轉並下墜<ref>{{cite web|title=Dua Kali Ledakan di Bawah Laut, Bupati: Pesawat Sriwijaya Air SJY 182 Jatuh|url=https://www.suara.com/news/2021/01/09/182735/dua-kali-ledakan-di-bawah-laut-bupati-pesawat-sriwijaya-air-sjy-182-jatuh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109161440/https://www.suara.com/news/2021/01/09/182735/dua-kali-ledakan-di-bawah-laut-bupati-pesawat-sriwijaya-air-sjy-182-jatuh|archive-date=2021-01-09|access-date=2021-01-09|publisher=Suara|language=id|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[航空管制員|航空管制員]]發現異樣后要求機師回報狀況，未果<ref>{{cite web|date=2021-01-09|title=Ini Kronologi Jatuhnya Pesawat Sriwijaya Air PK-CLC|url=https://nasional.sindonews.com/read/295672/15/ini-kronologi-jatuhnya-pesawat-sriwijaya-air-pk-clc-1610197297|access-date=2021-01-09|website=nasional.sindonews.com|language=id-ID|archive-date=2021-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109151643/https://nasional.sindonews.com/read/295672/15/ini-kronologi-jatuhnya-pesawat-sriwijaya-air-pk-clc-1610197297|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{lang|en|{{le|AirNav系統|AirNav RadarBox|AirNav}}}}系統的飛行數據顯示，下午2時40分飛機處於爬升階段時，突然從{{cvt|10900|ft}}急速下墜至{{cvt|7650|ft}}<ref name="AirLiveBreaking">{{cite web|date=2021-01-09|title=BREAKING Sriwijaya Air #SJ182 Boeing 737 disappeared from radars after takeoff|url=https://www.airlive.net/breaking-sriwijaya-air-sj182-boeing-737-disappeared-from-radars-after-takeoff/|access-date=2021-01-09|website=airlive.net|archive-date=2021-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109104253/https://www.airlive.net/breaking-sriwijaya-air-sj182-boeing-737-disappeared-from-radars-after-takeoff/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{lang|en|[[Flightradar24|Flightradar24]]}}則稱[[起飛|起飛]]後四分鐘，客機在少於一分鐘内就急劇下墜約{{cvt|10000|ft}}<ref>{{cite news|date=2021-01-09|title=FlightRadar24: Pesawat Sriwijaya Air Hilang Kontak 4 Menit Setelah Lepas Landas|language=id-ID|publisher=Detik News|url=https://news.detik.com/berita/d-5327331/flightradar24-pesawat-sriwijaya-air-hilang-kontak-4-menit-setelah-lepas-landas|access-date=2021-01-09|archive-date=2021-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109110634/https://news.detik.com/berita/d-5327331/flightradar24-pesawat-sriwijaya-air-hilang-kontak-4-menit-setelah-lepas-landas|dead-url=no}}</ref>。數據也顯示客機在下午2時40分08秒至14秒這六秒鐘之間下墜{{cvt|1755|ft}}，之後的兩秒鐘下墜{{cvt|825|ft}}，接下來的四秒鐘再墜落{{cvt|2725|ft}}，并在航程的最後七秒鐘内急速下降{{cvt|5150|ft}}<ref>{{cite web|date=2021-01-09|title=Sriwijaya Air flight 182 - Normal Resolution CSV File|url=https://www.flightradar24.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SJ182_26860e0e.csv|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109161249/https://www.flightradar24.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SJ182_26860e0e.csv|archive-date=2021-01-09|access-date=2021-01-09|publisher=Flightradar24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。可能由于[[阻力#空氣動力學中的阻力|滞空]][[自由落體#自由落体運動各物理量关系|重力]]及飞机自身[[空气动力学|动力]]的变化，此类因素相互作用的结果<ref>{{cite web |title=参考 |url=https://www.zaobao.com/znews/sea/story20210111-1115306 |website= |quote=澳大利亚一名航空事故调查专家戴尔说：‘很多人就出事飞机的最终下降速度作出评论，不过这虽然暗示飞机可能出故障，但确切的肇事原因还有待调查。事实上，导致飞机以那样快的速度下降的原因很多。’|accessdate=2021-01-15}}</ref>，客機急墜期間曾急劇變速，數秒鐘之内進行了加速及減速<ref>{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=2021-01-09|title=Sriwijaya Air Flight 182 - Granular CSV File|url=https://www.flightradar24.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SJ182_Granular_data_release.csv|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109161358/https://www.flightradar24.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/SJ182_Granular_data_release.csv|archive-date=2021-01-09|access-date=2021-01-10|website=[[Flightradar24|Flightradar24]]|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

下午2時40分27秒，[[Flightradar24|Flightradar24]]最後一次錄得客機數據，當時其飛行高度為{{cvt|250|ft}}<ref>{{cite web|date=2021-01-09|title=Sriwijaya Air flight 182 crashes near Jakarta|url=https://www.flightradar24.com/blog/sriwijaya-air-flight-182-crashes-near-jakarta/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109161316/https://www.flightradar24.com/blog/sriwijaya-air-flight-182-crashes-near-jakarta/|archive-date=2021-01-09|access-date=2021-01-09|publisher=Flightradar24|dead-url=no}}</ref>，隨後客機失去{{lang|en|[[ADS-B|ADS-B]]}}信号，當時其垂直速度达-30720英尺每分鐘（-561千米每小时）。182號航班最後一次與航空管制員聯係為下午2時40分。客機被證實墜毀於蘇加諾-哈達國際機場以北{{cvt|19|km}}處的爪哇海<ref>{{cite web|last=Ranter|first=Harro|date=2021-01-09|title=ASN Aircraft accident Boeing 737-524 (WL) PK-CLC Jakarta-Soekarno-Hatta International Airport (CGK)|url=https://aviation-safety.net/database/record.php?id=20210109-0|access-date=2021-01-09|work=Flight Safety Foundation|publisher=Aviation Safety Network|archive-date=2021-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211205013854/https://aviation-safety.net/database/record.php?id=20210109-0|dead-url=no}}</ref>，墜毀位置位於拉基島附近<ref>{{cite news|date=2021-01-09|title=Menhub Pastikan Sriwijaya Air SJY-182 Jatuh di Dekat Pulau Laki|language=id|publisher=Detik News|url=https://news.detik.com/berita/d-5327392/menhub-pastikan-sriwijaya-air-sjy-182-jatuh-di-dekat-pulau-laki|access-date=2021-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109161438/https://news.detik.com/berita/d-5327392/menhub-pastikan-sriwijaya-air-sj182-jatuh-di-dekat-pulau-laki|archive-date=2021-01-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。航空管制員稱飛機在整段航程中從未發出過如{{lang|en|[[pan-pan|pan-pan]]}}或{{lang|en|[[Mayday|Mayday]]}}的求救信號。{{tsl|id|Kementerian Perhubungan Republik Indonesia|印尼交通运输部}}官員也稱飛機偏离既定航线，由本来的东北方向转向西北方向<ref>{{cite news|date=2021-01-10|title=◤印尼空难◢印尼客机坠落路线曝光-漏夜搜救寻获|language=zh-hans|publisher=[[中國報|中國報]]|url=https://www.chinapress.com.my/20210110/%E2%97%A4%E5%8D%B0%E5%B0%BC%E7%A9%BA%E9%9A%BE%E2%97%A2%E5%8D%B0%E5%B0%BC%E5%AE%A2%E6%9C%BA%E5%9D%A0%E8%90%BD%E8%B7%AF%E7%BA%BF%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89-%E6%BC%8F%E5%A4%9C%E6%90%9C%E6%95%91%E5%AF%BB%E8%8E%B7/|access-date=2021-01-10|archive-date=2021-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110150759/https://www.chinapress.com.my/20210110/%E2%97%A4%E5%8D%B0%E5%B0%BC%E7%A9%BA%E9%9A%BE%E2%97%A2%E5%8D%B0%E5%B0%BC%E5%AE%A2%E6%9C%BA%E5%9D%A0%E8%90%BD%E8%B7%AF%E7%BA%BF%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89-%E6%BC%8F%E5%A4%9C%E6%90%9C%E6%95%91%E5%AF%BB%E8%8E%B7/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 机组与乘客 ==
班机载有62人，以及行李貨物{{cvt|500|kg}}<ref name="AirLiveBreaking"/>。包括50名乘客（40名成人，7名儿童，3名婴儿）和12名機組人員，均爲[[印度尼西亞人|印度尼西亞公民]]<ref name="Penumpang"/><ref name="Kru"/><ref name="Twelve"/><ref>[http://www.facebook.com/SriwijayaAir/posts/4069180669759010 Media Statement: Informasi Penerbangan Sriwijaya Air SJ-182] {{Wayback|url=http://www.facebook.com/SriwijayaAir/posts/4069180669759010 |date=20210216082056 }}（Sriwijava Air Facebook專頁，2020年1月10日）（附：[http://www.instagram.com/p/CJ0-SzSDFWa Instagram 貼文] {{Wayback|url=http://www.instagram.com/p/CJ0-SzSDFWa |date=20210324134336 }}）</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=印尼一航班坠毁：为波音737飞机，至少载有62人 |url=https://wallstreetcn.com/articles/3616496 |website=华尔街见闻 |accessdate=2021-01-10 |archive-date=2021-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210923085011/https://wallstreetcn.com/articles/3616496 |dead-url=no }}</ref>{{R|新华网1}}。印尼华文媒体《[[国际日报|国际日报]]》指航班乘客多为[[印度尼西亞華人|华人]]<ref>{{cite news |title=印尼失事客机罹难者残骸寻获 |url=https://www.zaobao.com.sg/realtime/world/story20210110-1115205 |access-date=2021-01-10 |publisher=[[联合早报|联合早报]] |date=2021-01-10 |language=zh-hans |archive-date=2021-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210923083242/https://www.zaobao.com.sg/realtime/world/story20210110-1115205 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。印尼政黨{{le|人民良心黨|People's Conscience Party}}成员、{{tsl|id| Himpunan Mahasiswa Islam|印尼伊斯兰大学生协会}}前主席{{le|穆利亚迪|Mulyadi Tamsir}}亦是乘客之一<ref>{{cite web|title=Kader Hanura Turut Jadi Korban Jatuhnya Sriwijaya Air Rute Jakarta-Pontianak|url=https://www.beritasatu.com/politik/718159/kader-hanura-turut-jadi-korban-jatuhnya-sriwijaya-air-rute-jakartapontianak|publisher=Berita Satu|access-date=2021-01-09|language=id|archive-date=2021-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110150829/https://www.beritasatu.com/politik/718159/kader-hanura-turut-jadi-korban-jatuhnya-sriwijaya-air-rute-jakartapontianak|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=3 Keluarga TNI AU Jadi Penumpang Pesawat Sriwijaya Air SJ182 yang Jatuh|url=https://news.detik.com/berita/d-5327531/3-keluarga-tni-au-jadi-penumpang-pesawat-sriwijaya-air-sj182-yang-jatuh?tag_from=wp_hl_judul|publisher=Detik News|access-date=2021-01-09|archive-date=2021-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109161354/https://news.detik.com/berita/d-5327531/3-keluarga-tni-au-jadi-penumpang-pesawat-sriwijaya-air-sj182-yang-jatuh?tag_from=wp_hl_judul|dead-url=no}}</ref>。受[[2019冠状病毒病|2019冠状病毒病]]的[[2019冠状病毒病印度尼西亚疫情|影响]]，乘坐飞机的成本又附加上[[2019冠状病毒病检测|检测]]费用超出一般家庭的负担能力，致使一些原本计划搭乘该趟航班的旅客转而选择了其他费用较低的旅行方式<ref>{{cite web |title= 因冠病检测费太贵 一家八口放弃搭机逃死劫 |url= https://www.zaobao.com.sg/znews/sea/story20210112-1115588 |accessdate= 2021-01-13 |archive-date= 2021-09-23 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210923081746/https://www.zaobao.com.sg/znews/sea/story20210112-1115588 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

12名機組人員中只有六人執飛該航班，另外六名機組人員則隨行。[[机长|机长]]阿夫萬·占扎米（{{lang|en|Afwan Zamzami}}）<ref group=注> 阿夫萬（{{lang|en|Afwan}}）是一个印尼语[[无姓氏|单名]]，在印尼作为[[印度尼西亚人名|人名]]较常见</ref>曾是印尼空军飞行员，[[副機師|副機師]]則爲2013年加入三佛齐航空的迪耶戈·马穆伊特（{{lang|en|Diego Mamahit}}），两人有丰富飞行经验<ref name="AirLive">{{cite web|title=PK-CLC Sriwijaya Air Boeing 737-524(WL)|url=https://www.planespotters.net/airframe/boeing-737-500-pk-clc-sriwijaya-air/rovwz3|access-date=2021-01-09|publisher=Planespotters|archive-date=2021-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109161027/https://www.planespotters.net/airframe/boeing-737-500-pk-clc-sriwijaya-air/rovwz3|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|date=2021-01-09|title=Sriwijaya Air SJY 182 Hilang Kontak Bawa 56 Penumpang Termasuk 3 Bayi|language=id|publisher=Suara|url=https://www.suara.com/news/2021/01/09/175802/sriwijaya-air-sjy-182-hilang-kontak-bawa-56-penumpang-termasuk-3-bayi|access-date=2021-01-09|archive-date=2021-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109161320/https://www.suara.com/news/2021/01/09/175802/sriwijaya-air-sjy-182-hilang-kontak-bawa-56-penumpang-termasuk-3-bayi|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Pilot Sriwijaya Air yang Hilang Kontak Merupakan Mantan Penerbang TNI AU|url=https://nasional.kompas.com/read/2021/01/09/21425741/pilot-sriwijaya-air-yang-hilang-kontak-merupakan-mantan-penerbang-tni-au|publisher=Kompas|access-date=2021-01-09|archive-date=2021-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109161323/https://nasional.kompas.com/read/2021/01/09/21425741/pilot-sriwijaya-air-yang-hilang-kontak-merupakan-mantan-penerbang-tni-au|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其余四人则是[[空中乘务员|空中乘务员]] <ref>{{cite news|last=|first=|date=9 January 2021|title=Sriwijaya Air SJY 182 Hilang Kontak Bawa 56 Penumpang Termasuk 3 Bayi|language=id|publisher=Suara|url=https://www.suara.com/news/2021/01/09/175802/sriwijaya-air-sjy-182-hilang-kontak-bawa-56-penumpang-termasuk-3-bayi|access-date=2021-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109161320/https://www.suara.com/news/2021/01/09/175802/sriwijaya-air-sjy-182-hilang-kontak-bawa-56-penumpang-termasuk-3-bayi|archive-date=2021-01-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。随行的六名机组成员与部分乘客来自早先抵达苏加诺国际机场并进港停泊的[[楠航空|楠航空]]班机<ref>{{cite web|title=Fakta Sementara Manifes Sriwijaya Air SJ 182: Kru NAM Air hingga Adanya Penumpang Pakai Identitas Orang Lain Halaman all|trans-title=Temporary Facts About Sriwijaya Air SJ 182 Manifest: NAM Air Crew and Passengers Using Other People's Identities Page all|url=https://megapolitan.kompas.com/read/2021/01/12/17283461/fakta-sementara-manifes-sriwijaya-air-sj-182-kru-nam-air-hingga-adanya|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113120549/https://megapolitan.kompas.com/read/2021/01/12/17283461/fakta-sementara-manifes-sriwijaya-air-sj-182-kru-nam-air-hingga-adanya|archive-date=2021-01-13|access-date=2021-02-01|website=megapolitan.kompas.com|publisher=Kompas Cyber Media|language=id|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Safitri|first=Eva|date=|title=Sriwijaya Air Jelaskan Pengalihan Penumpang NAM Air ke Penerbangan SJ182|trans-title=Sriwijaya Air Explains the Transfer of NAM Air Passengers to Flight SJ182|url=https://news.detik.com/berita/d-5328721/sriwijaya-air-jelaskan-pengalihan-penumpang-nam-air-ke-penerbangan-sj182|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113120552/https://news.detik.com/berita/d-5328721/sriwijaya-air-jelaskan-pengalihan-penumpang-nam-air-ke-penerbangan-sj182|archive-date=2021-01-13|access-date=2021-02-01|website=news.detik.com|publisher=Detik News|language=id|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
