== 事故调查 ==

参与救援与搜寻工作的{{tsl|id|Badan Nasional Pencarian dan Pertolongan|印尼国家搜索救助局}}立即将这起事故报告至{{tsl|id|Komite Nasional Keselamatan Transportasi|印尼运输安全委员会}}（KNKT），委员会派出搜救船{{lang|id|MV Baruna Jaya}}进行搜救支援。这艘船也参与过[[狮子航空610号班机空难|2018年狮航610班机空难]]和[[印尼亚洲航空8501号班机空难|2014年印尼亚航8501班机空难]]的搜救<ref>{{cite web |title=Kapal Khusus Baruna Jaya Disiapkan Cari Sriwijaya Air SJ182 |url=https://news.detik.com/berita/d-5327442/kapal-khusus-baruna-jaya-disiapkan-cari-sriwijaya-air-sj182?tag_from=wp_nhl_9 |publisher=Detik |language=id |accessdate=2020-01-09 |archive-date=2021-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109161503/https://news.detik.com/berita/d-5327442/kapal-khusus-baruna-jaya-disiapkan-cari-sriwijaya-air-sj182?tag_from=wp_nhl_9 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1月10日宣布开始搜寻[[飛行紀錄儀#記錄器|飞行数据记录器]]和[[飛行紀錄儀#記錄器|驾驶舱通话记录器]]（黑匣子）<ref>{{citeweb|title=Minggu, KNKT Cari Black Box Pesawat Sriwijaya Air yang Jatuh di Kepulauan Seribu|url=https://www.msn.com/id-id/berita/nasional/minggu-knkt-cari-black-box-pesawat-sriwijaya-air-yang-jatuh-di-kepulauan-seribu/ar-BB1cBFGp|publisher=Kompas|accessdate=2020-01-09|archive-date=2021-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109161425/https://www.msn.com/id-id/berita/nasional/minggu-knkt-cari-black-box-pesawat-sriwijaya-air-yang-jatuh-di-kepulauan-seribu/ar-BB1cBFGp|dead-url=no}}</ref>。随后因爲墜毀的波音客機是由美國製造，作为客机制造国的[[美国国家运输安全委员会|美国国家运输安全委员会]]表明将加入搜寻<ref>{{citeweb|title=Investigasi Penyebab Sriwijaya Air SJ182 Jatuh, KNKT Koordinasi dengan NTSB Amerika|url=https://www.inews.id/news/nasional/investigasi-penyebab-sriwijaya-air-sj182-jatuh-knkt-koordinasi-dengan-ntsb-amerika|publisher=INews|accessdate=2020-01-10|archive-date=2021-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109221527/https://www.inews.id/news/nasional/investigasi-penyebab-sriwijaya-air-sj182-jatuh-knkt-koordinasi-dengan-ntsb-amerika|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1月12日，搜救人員將發現的飞行数据记录器打撈上岸，同时发现的还有一个分离的原本连至驾驶舱通话记录器的-{zh-cn:{{tsl|en|radio beacon|无线电信标}};zh-tw:{{tsl|en|radio beacon|無線電指標}}}-，这预示失事客机的另一个记录器也在附近海域<ref>{{cite news|title=印尼海军找到失事飞机黑匣子|url=https://news.sina.com.cn/w/2021-01-12/doc-ikftpnnx6148095.shtml|accessdate=2021-01-12|archive-date=2021-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324140120/https://news.sina.com.cn/w/2021-01-12/doc-ikftpnnx6148095.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=|title=Isi Black Box Sriwijaya Air Berhasil Diunduh KNKT, Apa Isinya?|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/BigStory12/idUSKBN29H0AF|publisher=Reuters|access-date=2021-01-12|language=en|archive-date=2021-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210923081859/https://www.reuters.com/article/BigStory12/idUSKBN29H0AF|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title= 印尼海军找到失事客机飞行数据记录器|url=https://www.zaobao.com/realtime/world/story20210112-1115802|publisher=联合早报|access-date=2021-01-12|language=zh-hans}}</ref>。搜寻人员表示，驾驶舱通话记录器记录数据的记忆单元已从外壳脱落，因此极有可能已陷入[[海床|海床]]2-3米深，寻获的难度也随之变大<ref name="CO1">{{citeweb|author=Richard C. Paddock|author2=Muktita Suhartono|title=What Made the Indonesian Plane Crash? New Report Sheds Light|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/02/10/world/asia/indonesia-plane-crash-report.html|publisher=NYT|date=2021-02-22|accessdate=2020-03-05|archive-date=2021-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210514104643/https://www.nytimes.com/2021/02/10/world/asia/indonesia-plane-crash-report.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2021年3月31日，印尼当局使用{{tsl|en|Trailing suction hopper dredger|耙吸式挖泥船}}成功打捞驾驶舱通话记录器，并将记录器送入实验室进行解读<ref>{{citeweb|title=Indonesia recovers cockpit voice recorder of crashed Sriwijaya Air jet|url=https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-recovers-cockpit-voice-recorder-crashed-sriwijaya-air-jet-2021-03-31/|publisher=Reuters|date=2021-03-31|accessdate=2020-03-31|archive-date=2021-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210517054731/https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-recovers-cockpit-voice-recorder-crashed-sriwijaya-air-jet-2021-03-31/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Akhirnya CVR Pesawat Siriwijaya Air SJ182 Berhasil Ditemukan|url=https://www.republika.co.id/berita/qqtcgj383/akhirnya-cvr-pesawat-siriwijaya-air-sj182-berhasil-ditemukan|publisher=Republika|language=id|access-date=2021-07-16|archive-date=2021-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210716100222/https://www.republika.co.id/berita/qqtcgj383/akhirnya-cvr-pesawat-siriwijaya-air-sj182-berhasil-ditemukan|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=CVR Sriwijaya Air SJ182 Ditemukan 500 Meter dari Pulau Laki|url=https://news.detik.com/berita/d-5514943/cvr-sriwijaya-air-sj182-ditemukan-500-meter-dari-pulau-laki|publisher=Detik|language=id|access-date=2021-07-16|archive-date=2021-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210718231657/https://news.detik.com/berita/d-5514943/cvr-sriwijaya-air-sj182-ditemukan-500-meter-dari-pulau-laki|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

三佛齊航空的总经理杰斐逊（Jefferson Jauwena）确认，起飞前飞机保养完好，性能正常<ref name=jk/>，{{tsl|id|Kementerian Perhubungan Republik Indonesia|印尼交通运输部}}也证实了这种说法<ref>{{cite web|title=Kemenhub: Sebelum Celaka, Pesawat Sriwijaya Air Boeing 737–500 dalam Kondisi Laik Terbang|url=https://www.msn.com/id-id/berita/other/kemenhub-sebelum-celaka-pesawat-sriwijaya-air-boeing-737-500-dalam-kondisi-laik-terbang/ar-BB1cFe32|publisher=MSN|access-date=12 January 2020|archive-date=2021-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113120700/https://www.msn.com/id-id/berita/other/kemenhub-sebelum-celaka-pesawat-sriwijaya-air-boeing-737-500-dalam-kondisi-laik-terbang/ar-BB1cFe32|dead-url=no}}</ref>。杰斐逊也表示，超过25年的机龄导致飞机耐空性下降可能是事故的一个原因，而早前[[美国联邦航空管理局|美国联邦航空管理局]]已对波音737–500系飞机的操作者发布了针对该型飞机左{{tsl|en|Nacelle|发动机短舱}}部件[[金属疲劳|金属疲劳]]情况的[[适航指令|适航指令]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Airworthiness Directives; The Boeing Company Airplanes|url=https://www.federalregister.gov/documents/2020/12/23/2020-28270/airworthiness-directives-the-boeing-company-airplanes|publisher=Federal Aviation Administration|date=23 December 2020|access-date=12 January 2021|archive-date=2021-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113121447/https://www.federalregister.gov/documents/2020/12/23/2020-28270/airworthiness-directives-the-boeing-company-airplanes|dead-url=no}} {{PD-notice}}</ref>。他并指出飞机起飞前的延误不是因为机械故障，而是由于天气的影响。KNKT表示将与[[印度尼西亚气象、气候和地球物理局|印尼气象、气候和地球物理局]]（BMKG）一同查明飞机在事故发生时遭遇的天气情况<ref>{{citeweb|title=Direktur Utama: Sriwijaya Air SJ182 Laik Terbang|url=https://www.liputan6.com/bisnis/read/4458135/isi-black-box-sriwijaya-air-berhasil-diunduh-knkt-apa-isinya|publisher=Medcom|archive-date=2021-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109161457/https://www.medcom.id/nasional/daerah/RkjlMEwN-direktur-utama-sriwijaya-air-sj182-laik-terbang|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

BMKG处的数据显示飞机可能遭遇[[湍流|湍流]]，飞机起飞过程中，降雨量为[[雨#等级|中至大雨]]并有[[雷|雷]]，苏加诺-哈达国际机场上空周围有{{cvt|15|km}}厚的[[积雨云|积雨云]]，{{tsl|en|Cloud top|云顶 (气象)|云顶}}气温为{{cvt|−70|°C}}，[[能见度|能见度]]据报告为{{cvt|2|km}}<ref>{{cite web|title=Seperti Apa Kondisi Cuaca Saat Sriwijaya SJ182 Air Jatuh?|url=https://news.detik.com/berita/d-5328426/seperti-apa-kondisi-cuaca-saat-sriwijaya-sj182-air-jatuh|publisher=Detik News|language=id|access-date=10 January 2021|archive-date=2021-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110151330/https://news.detik.com/berita/d-5328426/seperti-apa-kondisi-cuaca-saat-sriwijaya-sj182-air-jatuh|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[印度尼西亚国家航空航天研究所|印尼国家航空航天研究所]]（LAPAN）的观测数据则显示尽管天气状况较恶劣，但尚未达到极端的程度。在飞机起飞前稍早的11时正，爪哇海附近曾有一个{{tsl|en|Mesoscale convective system|中尺度对流系}}形成，但至起飞时该对流系已消散<ref>{{cite web|title=LAPAN: Tak Ada Awan Ekstrem Saat Sriwijaya Air Hilang Kontak|url=https://www.msn.com/id-id/berita/teknologidansains/lapan-tak-ada-awan-ekstrem-saat-sriwijaya-air-hilang-kontak/ar-BB1cCZs2|publisher=Tempo|access-date=10 January 2021|archive-date=2021-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111060926/https://www.msn.com/id-id/berita/teknologidansains/lapan-tak-ada-awan-ekstrem-saat-sriwijaya-air-hilang-kontak/ar-BB1cCZs2|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

对于飞机受疫情影响的长期停飞，一位印尼航空专家表示在2020年3月23日至10月23日，飞机入库进行了检修养护，因此有着良好的维护记录<ref name=":2">{{cite web|title=Pengamat soal Sriwijaya Air Jatuh: Tak Terkait Usia Pesawat|url=https://www.cnnindonesia.com/nasional/20210110075606-20-591671/pengamat-soal-sriwijaya-air-jatuh-tak-terkait-usia-pesawat|publisher=CNN Indonesia|access-date=10 January 2021|archive-date=2021-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110011717/https://www.cnnindonesia.com/nasional/20210110075606-20-591671/pengamat-soal-sriwijaya-air-jatuh-tak-terkait-usia-pesawat|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而另有专家质疑指，飞机的长时停放可能造成设备长期不运转，进而加剧机械结构问题的恶化<ref name="NYT 210113">{{cite news|last1=Ramzy|first1=Austin|last2=Sijabat|first2=Dera Menra|title=Indonesian Plane Went From No Flights to 132 in Less Than a Month|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/01/13/world/asia/indonesian-plane-crash-mothball.html|access-date=13 January 2021|newspaper=The New York Times|date=13 January 2021|archive-date=2021-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113120602/https://www.nytimes.com/2021/01/13/world/asia/indonesian-plane-crash-mothball.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Tele 210113">{{cite news|last1=Freeman|first1=Colin|title=Indonesia airliner crash may be linked to plane being grounded for nine months during lockdown|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2021/01/13/indonesian-airliner-crash-may-linked-plane-grounded-nine-months/|access-date=13 January 2021|newspaper=The Daily Telegraph|date=13 January 2021|archive-date=2021-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113183835/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2021/01/13/indonesian-airliner-crash-may-linked-plane-grounded-nine-months/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

由于飞机自起飞至失事经历的时间仅有数分钟，对空难原因的准确判断将极大依赖于[[飛行紀錄儀#記錄器|飞行数据记录器]]和[[飛行紀錄儀#記錄器|驾驶舱通话记录器]]的记录。KNKT一位调查员表示，有鉴飞机残骸在水域中的分布十分密集，可以初步推断飞机未在半空中发生炸裂，而是在撞击水面后才解体<ref name=re/>。KNKT在深入分析后表示，综合Flightradar24数据和打捞出的机体[[涡轮风扇发动机|发动机]]基盘和[[涡轮叶片|扇叶]]的形态来看，已能坐实前述推测，且可进一步推断飞机即使受到影响，在{{cvt|250|ft}}高度处仍留有运动能力<ref>{{cite web|title=KNKT Menduga Mesin Sriwijaya Air SJ 182 Masih Hidup Sebelum Membentur Air|url=https://nasional.kompas.com/read/2021/01/12/13113191/knkt-menduga-mesin-sriwijaya-air-sj-182-masih-hidup-sebelum-membentur-air|access-date=2021-01-12|website=nasional.kompas.com|language=id|archive-date=2021-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113120643/https://nasional.kompas.com/read/2021/01/12/13113191/knkt-menduga-mesin-sriwijaya-air-sj-182-masih-hidup-sebelum-membentur-air|dead-url=no}}</ref>
。对飞行数据记录器中存有数据的分析显示，飞机的两具引擎在坠海时仍在继续运转<ref>{{cite web |author=Maulandy Rizky Bayu Kencana |title=Kapal Khusus Baruna Jaya Disiapkan Cari Sriwijaya Air SJ182 |url=https://news.detik.com/berita/d-5327442/kapal-khusus-baruna-jaya-disiapkan-cari-sriwijaya-air-sj182?tag_from=wp_nhl_9 |publisher=Liputan6 |language=id |accessdate=2020-01-15 |archive-date=2021-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109161503/https://news.detik.com/berita/d-5327442/kapal-khusus-baruna-jaya-disiapkan-cari-sriwijaya-air-sj182?tag_from=wp_nhl_9 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2021年2月10日，KNKT发布了关于这起空难的初步报告<ref>{{citeweb|title=KNKT Rilis Laporan Awal Investigasi Sriwijaya Air SJ 182 Besok, Nasib CVR?|trans-title=KNKT明日将发布SJ-182事故的初期调查报告，但CVR（驾驶舱通话记录器）呢？|url=https://bisnis.tempo.co/read/1431119/knkt-rilis-laporan-awal-investigasi-sriwijaya-air-sj-182-besok-nasib-cvr|publisher=Tempo|language=id|accessdate=2021-02-14|archive-date=2021-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210215191251/https://bisnis.tempo.co/read/1431119/knkt-rilis-laporan-awal-investigasi-sriwijaya-air-sj-182-besok-nasib-cvr|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{citeweb|title=Besok, KNKT Bakal Sampaikan Hasil Investigasi Awal dari Jatuhnya SJ-182|trans-title=明天NTSC将公布SJ-182班机坠毁事故的初步调查结果|url=https://nasional.sindonews.com/read/329570/15/besok-knkt-bakal-sampaikan-hasil-investigasi-awal-dari-jatuhnya-sj-182-1612854178|publisher=Sindo News|language=id|accessdate=2021-02-14|archive-date=2021-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210216064107/https://nasional.sindonews.com/read/329570/15/besok-knkt-bakal-sampaikan-hasil-investigasi-awal-dari-jatuhnya-sj-182-1612854178|dead-url=no}}</ref>，报告提到飞机引擎在运转中[[推力|推力]]失衡，导致机体急转，最终坠入海洋<ref name="CO1"/><ref>{{citeweb|title=Crashed Sriwijaya Air jet had engine thrust imbalance - preliminary report|url=https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/crashed-sriwijaya-air-jet-had-engine-thrust-imbalance-preliminary-report-2021-02-10/|publisher=Reuters|date=2021-02-10|accessdate=2020-03-31|archive-date=2021-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210504152150/https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/crashed-sriwijaya-air-jet-had-engine-thrust-imbalance-preliminary-report-2021-02-10/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Prelim>{{Cite web |url=http://knkt.dephub.go.id/knkt/ntsc_aviation/baru/pre/2021/PK-CLC%20Preliminary%20Report.pdf |title=KOMITE NASIONAL KESELAMATAN TRANSPORTASI REPUBLIC OF INDONESIA PRELIMINARY KNKT.21.01.01.04 Aircraft Accident Investigation Report PT. Sriwijaya Air Boeing 737-500; PK-CLC Near Kepulauan Seribu, Jakarta Republic of Indonesia 9 January 2021 |publisher=Komite Nasional Keselamatan Transportasi |accessdate=2021-02-14 |dead-url=yes |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220114160004/http://knkt.dephub.go.id/knkt/ntsc_aviation/baru/pre/2021/PK-CLC%20Preliminary%20Report.pdf |archive-date=2022-01-14 }}</ref>。

== 影响 ==
对于[[波音|波音公司]]来说，这起空难的时间点相当敏感。在[[波音737_MAX|737MAX]]因系统问题发生的两起严重空难（[[狮子航空610号班机空难|狮子航空610号班机空难]]和[[埃塞俄比亚航空302号班机空难|埃塞俄比亚航空302号班机空难]]）而[[2019年波音737_MAX停飞事件|停飞]]将近2年后，才于2020年12月29日继[[南美洲|南美洲]]之后重新在重要市场[[美国|美国]]投入商用，标志着该型客机正常化运作的开始<ref>{{citeweb|url=https://www.npr.org/2020/12/29/951134212/boeing-737-max-completes-first-u-s-commercial-flight-since-it-was-grounded|title=Boeing 737 Max Completes 1st U.S. Commercial Flight Since It Was Grounded|website=npr.org|accessdate=2020-01-11|archive-date=2021-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211120152939/https://www.npr.org/2020/12/29/951134212/boeing-737-max-completes-first-u-s-commercial-flight-since-it-was-grounded|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而这起空难将不免再次引起公众质疑，但是失事[[波音737#737-500|波音737-524]]客机并未搭载与737MAX相同的系统，且已安全服役27年，因此波音公司的产品设计并不可能是导致空难的关键因素。波音公司也与引擎制造商[[通用电气|通用电气]]一同参与了失事客机的搜救行动，并对空难的发生表示了慰问<ref name=re/><ref>{{citeweb|url=https://boeing.mediaroom.com/news-releases-statements?item=130800|title=Boeing Statement on Sriwijaya Air Flight SJ-182|publisher=Boeing|date=2020-01-09|accessdate=2020-01-11|archive-date=2021-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210923082138/https://boeing.mediaroom.com/news-releases-statements?item=130800|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="bg">{{citenews|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2021-01-14/search-intensifies-for-black-box-of-doomed-sriwijaya-air-flight|title=Search Intensifies for Black Box of Doomed Sriwijaya Air Flight|publisher=Bloomberg|date=2020-01-14|accessdate=2020-01-15|archive-date=2021-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210201021904/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2021-01-14/search-intensifies-for-black-box-of-doomed-sriwijaya-air-flight|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

作为世界上最大的群岛国家，航空在[[印度尼西亚交通|印尼国内交通]]中占据重要位置。得益于庞大的人口与近年的经济增长刺激下产生的大量需求，印尼国内[[低成本航空公司|廉航产业]]迎来空前繁荣<ref name="TWB-ATPC">{{cite web | title = Data: Air transport, passengers carried | work = [[世界银行|世界银行]] | url = http://data.worldbank.org/indicator/IS.AIR.PSGR | access-date = 2021-01-15 | archive-date = 2022-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220119094705/https://data.worldbank.org/indicator/IS.AIR.PSGR | dead-url = no }}</ref>，但是其安全性也因一系列事件备受质疑<ref name="Aerotime-Indonesia">{{Cite web |url= http://aerotime.aero/special/can-indonesia-and-air-safety-become-synonymous-by-2019/ |title= Can Indonesia and air safety become synonymous by 2019? |website= aerotime.aero |language= en |access-date= 2021-01-15 |archive-date= 2021-09-23 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210923084718/https://aerotime.aero/special/can-indonesia-and-air-safety-become-synonymous-by-2019/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>，且拥有比较糟糕的过往安全记录<ref>{{cite news | url =http://www.smh.com.au/news/world/safety-woeful-admits-air-chief/2007/11/02/1193619119848.html | title =Safety woeful, admits air chief | newspaper =Sydney Morning Herald online | date =2 November 2007 | accessdate =2021-01-15 | archive-date =2018-02-28 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20180228161814/https://www.smh.com.au/news/world/safety-woeful-admits-air-chief/2007/11/02/1193619119848.html | dead-url =no }}</ref><ref name="SG2">{{cite web | title = 六年第三起重大空难 失事客机62人恐罹难印尼航安再受质疑 | work = 联合早报 | url = https://www.zaobao.com.sg/znews/sea/story20210111-1115306 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210115034509/https://www.zaobao.com.sg/znews/sea/story20210111-1115306 | archive-date = 2021-01-15 | accessdate = 2021-01-15 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。印尼因其“[[加鲁达印尼航空200号班机空难|未解决的安全疑虑]]”及未达国际安全标准而于2007年被列入[[欧盟|欧盟]]的[[被禁止進入歐盟成員國之航空公司列表|航空黑名单]]<ref>{{Cite news|last=Clark|first=Nicola|title=EU set to ban flights of Indonesia carriers|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=28 June 2007|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2007/06/28/world/europe/28iht-airlines.5.6398202.html|access-date=2021-01-15|archive-date=2016-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160720025551/http://www.nytimes.com/2007/06/28/world/europe/28iht-airlines.5.6398202.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，虽然随着问题的改善欧盟已于2018年将其从中完全移除<ref>{{Cite web|url= https://flightsafety.org/eu-lifts-ban-on-flights-by-indonesian-airlines/|title= EU Lifts Ban on Flights by Indonesian Airlines|website= flightsafety.org|language= en|access-date= 2021-01-15|archive-date= 2021-09-23|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210923082225/https://flightsafety.org/eu-lifts-ban-on-flights-by-indonesian-airlines/|dead-url= no}}</ref>，但是仍留有许多问题亟待解决，诸如恶性[[价格竞争|价格竞争]]和监管的缺失等<ref name="Tempo-1">{{cite news|newspaper=Tempo|author=Maria Yuniar|title=Deregulasi Penerbangan Picu Kepadatan Bandara|date=18 September 2013|url=http://bisnis.tempo.co/read/news/2013/09/18/090514430/deregulasi-penerbangan-picu-kepadatan-bandara|language=id|accessdate=2021-01-15|archive-date=2015-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222103910/http://bisnis.tempo.co/read/news/2013/09/18/090514430/deregulasi-penerbangan-picu-kepadatan-bandara|dead-url=no}}</ref>。继亚航和狮航的两起空难后，三佛齐航空班机的失事已是印尼在6年中的第三起民航领域的重大事故，印尼政府也因此面临改善航空监管评估的更大压力<ref name="SG2"/>。印尼交通运输部已下达指示，要求各航班检查与失事客机同系列的老旧机型<ref name="bg"/>。

